### Changed (2026-06-03 mobile alignment)

- Fixed small-screen header alignment so the QB Networks brand block (logo + Home link target) stays centered.
- Moved the navigation directly under the centered brand block on mobile by showing the menu list inline in the header stack.
- Removed the mobile Menu toggle button for this layout so users always see Home, Ethics, and Code of Conduct links below the brand.

